Myriam Miedzian (1991 Anchor Books/Doubleday New York)
3. "Men Are Not Cost-Effective" by June Stephenson (1995 Harper Perennial New
York)
4. "Why Men Hate Women" by Adam Jukes (1993 Free Association Books, London)

