It's great to see this conversation going on on the list. Feminist
bookstores are indeed a great resource, and really do need your support.

We publish a catalog that lists the names, addresses (email and URL) and
phone numbers of all the feminist bookstores in the U.S. and Canada -- and
includes many titles from feminist presses -- which is available at no
charge at your local feminist bookstore. It is also on the web at
http:\\www.FemBookNet.com.


