ABIGAILS-L.  Does the list still exist?  If so, I'd appreciate updated
information.  If it has officially died, I'd also appreciate
confirmation of that.  Please reply privately.  I'll make whatever info
I get available at the Gender-Related Electronic Forums site, which
includes descriptions of more than 300 women- and gender-related e-mail
lists and which also lists the changes made in the past month.

