As a feminist and the mother of a 13 year old girl I have been having
dreams about her as a sexual being.  Most of them involve a man who is not
kind or doesn't use protection and in my dream I end up threatening
castration.  What my dreams have helped me realize is that I need to talk
to my daughter about sex in an uncensored manner - not just the "this is
your clitoris, this is your vagina" which I have done, but more about my
own experiences discovering my sexuality.  --  If you could say ANYTHING to
a young woman about sex -
if you could be totally uncensored, what would you say?  Is anyone
familiar with the literature on this subject?  Please respond privately
unless you believe it would benefit other readers.
Carol Horwitz
chorwitz@blue.weeg.uiowa.edu
