Date:         Mon, 15 Dec 1997 14:51:09 -0500
Reply-To:     Women's Studies List <WMST-L@UMDD.UMD.EDU>
Sender:       Women's Studies List <WMST-L@UMDD.UMD.EDU>
From:         Jean Noble <jnoble@YORKU.CA>
Subject:      Re: course: growing up female
