Since I had asked this question two years ago, let me share the info
received at the time:
Most preferrred "incoming student" instead of freshman BUT since not all
freshmen are incoming students (transfers, PT etc.) the name offered was
"frosh" or the British "fresher" OR "first-year student."
I mix and match...

