Date:         Thu, 18 Dec 1997 06:50:35 -0500
Reply-To:     sandyl@nervm.nerdc.ufl.edu
Sender:       Women's Studies List <WMST-L@UMDD.UMD.EDU>
From:         Sandra Lorean <sandyl@NERVM.NERDC.UFL.EDU>
