On the issue of power and desire, Jessica Benjamin's *Bond of Love:
Psychoanalysis, Feminism, and the Problem of Domination* provides some
insights. While she interrogates the male/female domination/submission
paradigms, she also discusses how desire acts as a lubricant (so to speak)
in power relationships or expressions of power and submission.

Deborah Moreland
University of Texas at Dallas
