CALL FOR CONTRIBUTERS

The Fall 1998 issue of the William Carlos Williams Review will be a special
issue exploring the relationships between HD (Hilda Doolittle) and William
Carlos Williams.  Interested contributers should submit articles (@25 pp.)
by MARCH 1ST to:

Glen MacLeod
